                " POLARIZED SOURCE AND TARGET."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".POWDERED CA-O-17 IRRADIATED WITH FAST NEUTRONS TO",
                " GENERATE F-CENTRES AT A CONCENTRATION OF 3.E18",
                " PER GRAM. THE TECHNIQUE OF DYNAMIC POLARISATION,",
                " USING THE UNRESOLVED SOLID EFFECT, WAS USED."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DIFFR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " MAGNETISED FE-CO CRYSTALSUSED AS POLARISER AND",
                " ANALYSER. DIFFERENCE IN THE NEUTRON LARMOUR",
                " PRECESSION FREQUENCY WAS MEASURED FOR A POLARISED",
                " AND DEPOLARISED TARGET. SEVERAL MEASUREMENTS WITH",
                " POSITIVE AND NEGATIVE POLARIZATIONS WERE TAKEN."
              ]
            }
          ],
